						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Slab standing in the Siddhēśvara temple.</hi></p>						

						<p>Jagadēkamalla I (Jayasiṁha II)—date lost.</p>						

						<p>This badly worn out record refers itself to the reign of <hi rend="bold">Jagadēkamalla Jayasiṁha</hi> and to a Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara, Prachaṇḍa-daṇḍanāyaka (name lost). The date and other details of the record are lost. Only the imprecatory portion is extant.</p>						

